external.description:
Do you want a monster tamer game where the gameplay is like if Skylanders was blended with Warframe and Spore? If so, then Voidling Bound is the game for you! Created by Ex-Skylanders developers, Voidling Bound is a creature collector game with quite the gameplay twist. Unlike other games in the same genre which tend to be turn based RPGs, Voiding Bound goes in a very different direction. Instead, Voidling Bound is a third person shooter with RPG elements and multiple customizable elements. The world of Voidling Bound has humanity struggling against a parasitic force, with their only weapon being the Voidlings. To fight against the parasite menace, you must take direct control of these creatures through a neural bond. However, you don’t just control these Voidlings, as it is your job to both breed and customize them as well. With almost 47 different voidlings, you can either rescue eggs on missions, or selectively breed them for specific characteristics. As you use your voidlings more, you can level them up and improve their stats based on your play style and Voidling. No matter your build, it’s your job to craft your Voidling to be the ultimate parasite fighting machine. WHAT […]
